column20: Prominent - chased clear leader before 3 out - clear with one other after 2 out - pushed along and headway approaching last - led last - pushed out and ran on well towards finish(op 15/2)
Led 1st - clear 4 out - clear with one other 2 out - shaken up and reduced lead approaching last - jumped slightly right and headed last - no extra towards finish(op 1/6 tchd 2/15)
Towards rear - in touch with leaders halfway - went modest third after 2 out - soon no impression(op 11/1)
Prominent - dropped to midfield halfway - not fluent 3 out - soon went remote fourth - kept on - never on terms(tchd 28/1)
Towards rear - pecked on landing 3 out - weakened 2 out(op 100/1)
In touch with leaders - went second 7th - lost position before 3 out - weakened from 2 out
In rear - headway 4th - detached 4 out - unseated 3 out(op 80/1)
Unseated rider on way to start - towards rear - not fluent 1st - mistake and unseated 2nd
Led - not fluent 4th - not fluent 2nd - headed after 3rd - soon lost ground but in touch with leaders - headway before 5 out(tchd 4/5)
Towards rear - in touch with leaders after 4th(op 9/4)
Prominent - led after 3rd - headed after 4th - led again before 5 out(op 25/1)
In touch with leaders - headway before 3rd - led after 4th - headed before 5 out(op 11/2)
